; beep.ap: demonstrates the LCC+ `beep` trap.
; `beep` is an alias for `sound 2`: it plays the configured beep sound file,
; then falls back to a desktop default, then ASCII BEL (\x07).
; Run:  node src/plus/lccplus.js plusdemos/beep.ap
        .lccplus
        lea r0, msg
        sout r0
        nl
        beep            ; alias for sound 2
        halt
msg:    .string "beep.ap: playing the beep sound slot..."
